        separate-table approach (acm_person_assoc + acm_person_org_
        assoc) into a single polymorphic table (x_casemgmt_case_party).
        PersonAssociation.java is the primary semantic source for THIS
        FILE'S Person branch; PersonOrganizationAssociation.java is
        the primary semantic source for the Organization branch
